Name: Riese & Muller Superdelite5 GT Touring
Description: The Riese & Müller Superdelite5 GT Touring is a premium full-suspension e-bike designed for long-distance touring, comfort, and all-terrain capability. Featuring the Bosch Performance Line CX motor and the innovative DualBattery 1200 system—combining an 800 Wh PowerTube with a 400 Wh CompactTube—it offers exceptional range and powerful support for demanding rides. The Shimano CUES 11-speed drivetrain ensures smooth, reliable shifting, while high-end Fox suspension front and rear delivers outstanding control and comfort. With integrated Supernova lighting, TRP disc brakes, and RX Chip connectivity for smart features, the Superdelite5 GT Touring sets a new standard in performance, versatility, and long-range capability.

Name: Riese & Muller Superdelite5 GT Vario
Description: The Riese & Müller Superdelite5 GT Vario is a premium, long-range electric bike built for comfort, performance, and versatility on any terrain. Powered by the Bosch Performance Line CX motor and the DualBattery 1200 system—featuring an 800 Wh PowerTube and a 400 Wh CompactTube—it delivers an outstanding 1,200 Wh of total capacity for extended adventures. The Enviolo stepless gear hub paired with a low-maintenance Gates carbon belt drive offers smooth, silent shifting and a clean, worry-free ride. Full Fox suspension ensures control and comfort across varied surfaces, while TRP disc brakes and Supernova lighting provide safety and visibility. With RX Chip integration for smart connectivity, the Superdelite5 GT Vario is ideal for riders seeking effortless range and refined performance.

Name: Riese & Muller Superdelite5 GT Rohloff
Description: The Riese & Müller Superdelite5 GT Rohloff is the pinnacle of performance and endurance in the world of electric touring bikes. Featuring the powerful Bosch Performance Line CX motor and the DualBattery 1200 system—combining an 800 Wh PowerTube with a 400 Wh CompactTube—it delivers an exceptional 1,200 Wh of total battery capacity for ultra-long-range adventures. At its core is the electronically shifting Rohloff E-14 14-speed hub gear, renowned for its durability, precision, and virtually maintenance-free performance. Paired with a Gates carbon belt drive, it offers silent, seamless shifting even under load. With premium Fox suspension, TRP disc brakes, Supernova lighting, and integrated RX Chip connectivity (providing Connect Ride features), the Superdelite5 GT Rohloff is engineered for riders who demand the highest levels of reliability, comfort, and all-terrain capability.
